 Nam - 送李仲賓蕭方崖出使安南其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nghi%E1%BB%85m/author-WBjKpsbZn7AL_s86vNKjZA">Trần Nghiễm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-zD7mrwO-43MIHObHTaGOMw">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh tự - 送尚書柴莊卿序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/author-1_5YGABQESnAmYdOvhbEZQ">Lý Khiêm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
